    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Northwest Ithaca boasts the tallest single-drop waterfall east of the Rockies, a dramatic gorge that attracts hikers year-round.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        25
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northwest_Ithaca%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Spring in Northwest Ithaca brings rushing waterfalls and multi‑use trails that stay open all seasons, perfect for outdoor adventures.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        15
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.visitithaca.com/"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "The area’s winding, rugged gorge features notable Lucifer Falls, adding to the region’s collection of scenic cascades.",
